{"tha-ap421:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap421:0.2":"Bhaddalivagga ","tha-ap421:0.3":"Patthodanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap421:1.1":"“Vanacari pure asim, ","tha-ap421:1.2":"satatam vanakammiko; ","tha-ap421:1.3":"Patthodanam gahetvana, ","tha-ap421:1.4":"kammantam agamasaham. ","tha-ap421:2.1":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap421:2.2":"sayambhum aparajitam; ","tha-ap421:2.3":"Vana pindaya nikkhantam, ","tha-ap421:2.4":"disva cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap421:3.1":"Parakammayane yutto, ","tha-ap421:3.2":"punnanca me na vijjati; ","tha-ap421:3.3":"Ayam patthodano atthi, ","tha-ap421:3.4":"bhojayissamaham munim. ","tha-ap421:4.1":"Patthodanam gahetvana, ","tha-ap421:4.2":"sayambhussa adasaham; ","tha-ap421:4.3":"Mama nijjhayamanassa, ","tha-ap421:4.4":"paribhunji tada muni. ","tha-ap421:5.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap421:5.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap421:5.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap421:5.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap421:6.1":"Chattimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap421:6.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap421:6.3":"Tettimsakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap421:6.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap421:7.1":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap421:7.2":"gananato asankhiyam; ","tha-ap421:7.3":"Sukhito yasava homi, ","tha-ap421:7.4":"patthodanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap421:8.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap421:8.2":"labhami amitam dhanam; ","tha-ap421:8.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap421:8.4":"patthodanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap421:9.1":"Nadisotapatibhaga, ","tha-ap421:9.2":"bhoga nibbattare mama; ","tha-ap421:9.3":"Parimetum na sakkomi, ","tha-ap421:9.4":"patthodanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap421:10.1":"Imam khada imam bhunja, ","tha-ap421:10.2":"imamhi sayane saya; ","tha-ap421:10.3":"Tenaham sukhito homi, ","tha-ap421:10.4":"patthodanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap421:11.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap421:11.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap421:11.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap421:11.4":"patthodanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap421:12.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap421:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap421:12.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap421:13.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap421:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap421:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap421:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap421:14.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap421:14.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap421:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma patthodanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap421:16.1":"Patthodanadayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}